NAME
    Alien::pugixml - Find or build pugixml C++ XML parser library

SYNOPSIS
        use Alien::pugixml;
        use ExtUtils::MakeMaker;

        WriteMakefile(
            ...
            CONFIGURE_REQUIRES => {
                'Alien::pugixml' => 0,
            },
            CCFLAGS => Alien::pugixml->cflags,
            LIBS    => Alien::pugixml->libs,
        );

DESCRIPTION
    This module provides the pugixml C++ XML parsing library. It will either
    use the system library if available, or download and build it from
    source.

METHODS
    All methods are inherited from Alien::Base.

SEE ALSO
    Alien::Base, pugixml <https://pugixml.org/>

